XiZero Changelog
================


Changes from 0.1 to 0.2
-----------------------

+ dependency changed from fltk to (free)glut
+ audio dependency alut added
+ used image format changed from tga to ras
+ level map format changed from ascii to ras heightmap
+ xpm icons added
+ msgbox'es added
+ anti-aliased mode added
+ improved hardware detection
+ code size reduction
+ hundereds of bugs fixed
+ better commenting of classes
+ no more global variables
+ common base class with singleton optional capability
+ a lot of code restructuring
+ added a manpage
+ better desktop integration
